high_descs: turn around and face the kitchen counter on the right side of the sink
grab the spatula off of the sink
move left a bit and face the right side of the kitchen sink
clean off the spatula inside the sink
turn left to face the corner where the two kitchen counters meet
put the spatula inside of the pull out drawer on the right side corner where the two kitchen counters meet
anns.task_desc: put the spatula in a pull out drawer in the kitchen

high_descs: Go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Rinse the spatula off in the sink.
Turn to the drawer on the left.
Put the clean spatula in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward, then turn right to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the spatula on the counter, to the right of the sink.
Move to the sink, to your left.
Wash the spatula in the sink.
Turn left, open the drawer beneath the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the spatula in the open drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula in the drawer.
